1
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:49,840
A mere ant

2
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:52,479
trying to shake an elephant.

3
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,280
Ridiculous.

4
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:03,080
I will definitely find you.

5
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:12,040
Daughter, I...

6
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,360
Daughter,

7
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:17,000
I have been invited to a literary gathering at Yayuan Villa.

8
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:20,520
The master of the villa happens to be the youngest son of the former Deputy Magistrate Cao Shi,

9
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,040
Cao Wen.

10
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,240
At this gathering,

11
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,960
this 'Miscellaneous Records'

12
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:32,640
has been discussed by current scholars.

13
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:35,250
Some say it has opened up a new literary style,

14
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:38,280
while others condemn it as intolerably vulgar.

15
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,520
What exactly are you trying to say?

16
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:44,720
Look, I am tied up with official duties

17
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,240
and cannot go.

18
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:49,240
You should go on my behalf.

19
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:52,200
Take the opportunity to meet this Cao Wen.

20
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:55,160
Since you are a good match,

21
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:58,800
maybe it could lead to a wonderful marriage.

22
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,920
Your daughter

23
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:06,000
already has someone in her heart.

24
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:10,560
Daughter, are you talking about that Buliangren?

25
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,520
Let me tell you,

26
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:16,400
you are the daughter of the Deputy Magistrate.

27
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:19,320
Everything must be a good match in social status.

28
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:21,160
What do his parents do?

29
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:25,240
As the saying goes, like father, like son.

30
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:27,400
What if he... Okay, okay, Father.

31
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:30,079
Autopsies are my job,

32
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,280
and you want to interfere.

33
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:33,280
You also want to get involved in my marriage.

34
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,520
In this huge city of Luoyang,

35
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:37,160
there are so many things waiting for you to handle.

36
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,760
Please spare me.

37
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,760
In this huge city of Luoyang,

38
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,440
in my heart,

39
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,600
you are my greatest treasure.

40
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,720
Okay, I am your treasure.

41
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,920
I am your little treasure.

42
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:50,200
I am your big treasure.

43
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:51,600
Master.

44
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,800
Young Master Xu, son of Deputy Magistrate Xu of Chang'an, is here.

45
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,600
He says he came specifically to see our young lady.

46
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,920
Look, I'm getting old and forgetful.

47
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,480
How could I forget about Young Master Xu?

48
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:06,240
His father is the current Deputy Magistrate of Jingzhao.

49
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:08,480
Now that's what I call a good match.

50
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:11,400
Quick, invite him to the main hall.

51
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,760
Yes, Master.

52
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:15,200
I'll accept this invitation.

53
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:17,279
No time to lose, let's go now.

54
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,079
Daughter!

55
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,680
I'm off, Father!

56
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,880
You're making me work for nothing again!

57
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,720
Oh, you!

58
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,480
This invitation is for Commissioner Li.

59
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,760
It doesn't mention me.

60
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,520
My father has official duties,

61
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:38,560
so he wants us to go in his stead.

62
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:41,960
I was thinking you haven't been out for days,

63
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,240
so we might as well go together to relax.

64
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,840
It's fine.

65
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,400
I won't go this time.

66
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:52,120
I still have to sweep Sister Chunyi's grave.

67
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:54,960
If you go, be careful on the way.

68
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,800
We agreed. Why are you so slow to react?

69
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,760
Oops, I didn't react in time.

70
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,500
I didn't react in time either.

71
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,320
Why haven't you two left yet?

72
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:10,160
This villa is on the mountain and you have to cross the river.

73
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:12,800
If you are late, there will be no boat at the ferry.

74
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,680
Kids,

75
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,200
look what delicious food I brought.

76
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,120
Come here.

77
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,970
I'm telling you,

78
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,600
only scholars and literati are going this time.

79
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:25,240
The host of this poetry gathering is Cao Wen.

80
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,780
He is the son of the former Vice Governor Cao.

81
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:30,120
He is just 16 years old this year,

82
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:32,760
but he is already an excellent writer.

83
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,120
By the way, brat.

84
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,720
Talk less when you get there.

85
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,320
Don't make a fool of yourself

86
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:39,040
and become a laughingstock.

87
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,180
I have good literary talent too, Dad.

88
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:43,840
Mr. Su.

89
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,760
Yes.

90
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:48,610
Is this Cao Wen the son of the former Henan Vice Governor Cao Shi?

91
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:49,960
Exactly.

92
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:53,800
When Head Constable Qin solved the case of Vice Governor Cao,

93
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:55,940
he was still in his mother's womb.

94
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:59,920
I can't believe he is already 16.

95
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:04,000
And he's become a great scholar.

96
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:07,500
You should go to the elegant gathering early this time.

97
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,760
Once you get there,

98
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:12,000
you'll definitely experience their poetic sentiment and grace.

99
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,460
Talking more with these scholars and poets,

100
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,640
regarding your future literary attainments,

101
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:19,680
will definitely be of great benefit.

102
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:22,040
Could that fire back then

103
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:25,120
be connected to Vice Magistrate Cao's case?

104
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:29,080
Since Cao Wen is so talented,

105
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,920
I actually want to go and see.

106
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:34,200
Really? There you go again.

107
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:35,800
We have no time to lose.

108
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,330
Let's set off immediately.

109
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,880
You two must listen to Mr. Su.

110
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,920
I'll give you some candy when I get back.

111
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,159
Okay, got it.

112
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,120
Good kids. Hurry up, let's go.

113
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,840
Remember to practice your handwriting!

114
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:47,920
Alright, you may go.

115
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,800
Leave things here to me.

116
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,440
Mr. Su, we'll leave it to you.

117
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,120
Okay. Eat up.

118
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,360
I'm coming.

119
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,080
Be careful.

120
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:12,560
Come, Sister.

121
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:20,360
I am Li Jinglan, daughter of Vice Governor Li Ze.

122
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,320
This is our invitation.

123
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:25,080
These two are my close friends.

124
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:31,600
So it's Miss Li Jinglan, daughter of Vice Governor Li.

125
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:34,400
I will arrange someone to guide you right away.

126
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,440
Thank you.

127
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,600
I am Liu Renjiu.

128
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:41,440
I will guide you three distinguished guests to the villa to eat and rest.

129
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,880
The villa is located at the top of the mountain.

130
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:45,200
This is the only mountain road from the ferry crossing to the villa.

131
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,720
Please walk slowly, you three.

132
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,320
Thank you for your trouble.

133
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,040
After you.

134
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,440
Please.

135
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,560
Please.

136
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,360
This way.

137
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,880
Please.

138
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,880
This way.

139
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:23,280
I never tire of gazing at the green hills.

140
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:25,360
The flowing water holds endless charm.

141
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,280
The ancient temple bell echoes from afar.

142
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:30,040
The moon reflects coldly in the deep pool.

143
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,320
Oh.

144
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:34,240
The emerald ridges have boundless rhythm.

145
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:37,080
The clear breeze blows without end.

146
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:40,280
Birds chirp loudly in the secluded forest.

147
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:44,320
A waterfall flows fragrantly in the deep valley.

148
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,480
Mr. Lu,

149
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,720
what do you think?

150
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:52,760
The one in the green shirt on the left is Lu Yun, Vice Director of the Ministry of Rites.

151
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:55,960
His uncle was once the Minister of Revenue.

152
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:59,520
Mr. Lu is skilled at literary criticism.

153
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,200
He holds a position of the secondary sixth rank.

154
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:05,640
The one in the gray gown is Dong Tu, a compiler at Moxiang Bookstore.

155
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:08,560
Mr. Cao's book is printed by this bookstore.

156
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,000
This way.

157
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,720
The north wing is for the ladies.

158
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:20,360
The West and South wings are on the other side,

159
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,020
where the gentlemen can rest.

160
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,400
I shall show you two the way.

161
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,880
It's so far away.

162
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:28,400
Are there any other arrangements for today?

163
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,560
If you don't want to rest,

164
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,600
my lady has specifically ordered

165
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:33,320
that you can go to the main hall

166
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,840
to express yourselves,

167
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:35,840
drink wine, compose poems,

168
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,760
talk about everything,

169
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:38,320
and enjoy the fun together.

170
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,280
A grand banquet will be ready at noon.

171
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:42,520
Tomorrow morning, we will see you off.

172
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,100
Please enjoy yourselves.

173
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:47,120
Then let me rest for a moment.

174
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,720
I'll see you in the main hall.

175
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:50,720
Okay.

176
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,520
Please. Let's go.

177
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:55,000
You two, come with me.

178
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,280
Go ahead.

179
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,360
This way.

180
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:17,400
What a fragrant sweet wine.

181
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,280
You are indeed an expert, sir.

182
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:22,560
This wine is a carefully brewed rice wine.

183
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:25,160
It has the sweet aroma of fermented grain,

184
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:27,880
which slowly diffuses in the breeze.

185
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,360
Here you are, you two.

186
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,160
Thank you.

187
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:43,960
The temperature and time of this wine are just right.

188
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,680
The scenery outside the window remains the same.

189
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,040
No wonder people say

190
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:52,240
Yayuanju is a paradise.

191
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,920
Thank you for your praise, sir.

192
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:55,780
I thank you on behalf of the owner.

193
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,560
Please, this way.

194
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,000
Little constable,

195
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,600
you want to trick my Honglian?

196
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,160
No way.

197
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,240
Who lives in the East Wing?

198
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:16,040
Mrs. Cao and Young Master Cao live there.

199
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,680
Come, brother.

200
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,320
Please.

201
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:48,080
Madam, the guests have arrived.

202
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:52,200
Mrs. Cao, I am Li Jinglan.

203
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:54,540
My father, Li Ze, has official business,

204
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:56,440
so he sent me to visit.

205
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:58,800
I want to appreciate the great works at this gathering

206
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,120
to improve myself.

207
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:04,120
I've heard Miss Li rarely visits here

208
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:06,920
and has a generous and righteous nature.

209
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,480
It is my honor

210
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:11,000
that you could come today.

211
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,840
May I ask who the two behind you are?

212
00:12:14,160 --> 00:12:15,840
These are my friends,

213
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:18,480
Constable Su and Envoy Jueming.

214
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:21,280
Since they are your friends,

215
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:23,280
please take the seats of honor, all three of you.

216
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:26,120
Our banquet is about to begin.

217
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,120
Thank you.

218
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,600
Please.

219
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,920
Honored guests,

220
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,000
thank you for coming to the manor.

221
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,960
I invited you all here today

222
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:58,300
because my son has published a new collection of writings.

223
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:01,480
For my son's book to be published,

224
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:07,080
I truly must thank Yuan Zheng, the owner of Moxiang Bookstore.

225
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:11,280
Mr. Yuan's Moxiang Bookstore printed the collection for my son,

226
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:13,120
and deserves much credit.

227
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:15,240
You flatter me, Madam.

228
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,720
How could I claim the credit?

229
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:19,080
It's truly because your son is exceptionally talented,

230
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:21,280
writing as if guided by the gods.

231
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,640
Compiler Dong Tu and I...

232
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:25,720
I just put in a little effort

233
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:27,440
and did some organizing

234
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:30,280
so this masterpiece could be published.

235
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:31,960
It was my duty.

236
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:33,600
Not worth mentioning.

237
00:13:45,880 --> 00:13:46,880
Jueming.

238
00:13:47,800 --> 00:13:50,240
You said you met him before.

239
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,000
When was that?

240
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:57,700
He was the one who took Honglian away during the Lu Troupe's performance.

241
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,360
I remember now.

242
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:01,560
Honglian's father.

243
00:14:01,760 --> 00:14:03,080
Why is he here?

244
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:05,120
He's not very educated.

245
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:11,000
My son's new book has been published.

246
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:13,720
I wonder if you have read it.

247
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:15,280
He is still young.

248
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:18,520
I hope you can give him some advice.

249
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:25,560
I think the novel style of this book

250
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,240
is amazing.

251
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,720
It's a big breakthrough.

252
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,920
In the vast sea of literature,

253
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:35,680
he has opened a path that no one has ever walked before.

254
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:39,000
Brother Caowen is truly a genius.

255
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:41,280
I don't think so.

256
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:43,960
This book is terrible.

257
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,560
It has no structure.

258
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:48,160
The content is absurd

259
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:50,240
and harbors malicious intent.

260
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:52,200
It is alarming

261
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:53,960
and truly not a good book.

262
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,800
Please. Absurd.

263
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:11,240
A book's merit lies not in its form, but its substance.

264
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:14,800
If the story is interesting and the words are meaningful,

265
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:16,680
it is a good book.

266
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:21,040
Calling it terrifying or unorganized

267
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:24,760
is merely a narrow-minded view.

268
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:27,080
Scholar Jiang makes sense.

269
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:28,640
Very reasonable.

270
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:33,040
Scholar Jiang, please sit.

271
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:43,000
This is Jiang Shan, a scholar of Jixian Academy,

272
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,360
a subordinate fifth-rank official.

273
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:46,160
If any refined scholar wishes to write a book,

274
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,920
they all must seek his help.

275
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:52,560
I poured my heart and soul into this book.

276
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:55,360
I am fortunate that you elders have taken the time to come today.

277
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,640
I sincerely hope to exchange ideas with you all,

278
00:15:57,640 --> 00:15:59,280
and listen to your brilliant views.

279
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:01,440
It is truly my life's honor.

280
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:04,160
Mr. Cao.

281
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:06,680
I am just speaking my mind.

282
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:09,160
Please forgive me.

283
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,680
It doesn't matter.

284
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:16,000
Since it is a discussion,

285
00:16:16,680 --> 00:16:20,240
I would like to seek some advice from Mr. Cao.

286
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:24,000
Everything written in this book is about palace secrets.

287
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:27,000
It is hard to fathom without personal experience.

288
00:16:28,040 --> 00:16:29,600
You are still young.

289
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:32,480
How could you have such a writing style?

290
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:37,240
I...

291
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:41,680
It's just that...

292
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:46,680
I told him the fantasies and anecdotes I heard.

293
00:16:46,760 --> 00:16:50,400
He mixed them together with a bit of his talent,

294
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:52,760
and wrote this collection.

295
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:57,760
So it was the Madam's guidance

296
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,320
that led to such a masterpiece.

297
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:02,280
Extraordinary. Truly extraordinary.

298
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:05,680
Just treat it as a pastime after a meal.

299
00:17:05,839 --> 00:17:08,800
Everyone, please enjoy the food and drinks.

300
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,200
Come.

301
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:13,319
I offer a toast to everyone.

302
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:15,170
Let's drink this cup together.

303
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:17,260
Come, let's drink this cup together.

304
00:17:17,280 --> 00:17:19,010
Let's drink this cup together.

305
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:41,200
There's really no such thing as a free lunch in this world.

306
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,760
Who would have thought that after the meal,

307
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:44,680
Mrs. Cao would make each of us write a postscript

308
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,540
about how exquisite this book is?

309
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:47,600
This book is so thick.

310
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:50,440
If we don't finish writing, we won't be able to go back tomorrow.

311
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:52,160
If you want to write a postscript,

312
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,840
you don't necessarily have to read the book.

313
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:54,760
Why?

314
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:01,640
Mrs. Cao

315
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,960
just hopes everyone will put in a good word

316
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:06,080
to make her son's book sell better.

317
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:10,560
This way, her son's reputation will grow bigger and bigger.

318
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:12,240
As to whether you've read the book,

319
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,570
she doesn't care at all.

320
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,680
You just need to say a few nice words,

321
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:17,410
and she'll be fully satisfied.

322
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,000
I see.

323
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:20,760
Then I can get some sleep tonight.

324
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:21,880
Don't copy everything from me.

325
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:22,760
Think for yourself.

326
00:18:22,760 --> 00:18:25,160
I'm just using it for reference. Honestly.

327
00:18:26,360 --> 00:18:28,000
Someone is dead!

328
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,360
Help!

329
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:32,000
Someone come quickly. There's a dead body.

330
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:34,040
Someone is dead.

331
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,720
It wasn't me.

332
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:49,640
Someone is dead. It wasn't me. It wasn't me.

333
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,050
You can see the body now.

334
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:52,000
Mhm.

335
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:59,200
Lock down the entire villa immediately.

336
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,560
No one is allowed to leave.

337
00:19:00,560 --> 00:19:02,480
Lock down all exits of the villa immediately. Okay.

338
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:04,000
Hurry up.

339
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:12,800
'The Plot of False Pregnancy' Chapter One.

340
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:17,220
During the Tianbao era of the Tang Dynasty, Daming Palace stood in Chang'an.

341
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:19,760
I told you to accompany Consort Xian for a walk.

342
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:21,000
Look at what you did.

343
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:22,720
You actually let her fall.

344
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:25,400
What use are you to me? What use?

345
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:30,880
Madam.

346
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:35,000
Get out!

347
00:19:41,040 --> 00:19:42,200
Madam,

348
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:44,080
we couldn't save the baby.

349
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:49,560
This is royal blood.

350
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:51,240
How could you not save it?

351
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:53,520
How could it not be saved?

352
00:19:53,760 --> 00:19:55,160
It's too late.

353
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,120
Stop.

354
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:18,520
This child is of utmost importance.

355
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:20,200
Don't act recklessly.

356
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:22,380
Report it truthfully to the Emperor.

357
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:31,840
Do you still remember the joy we shared in bed?

358
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:35,640
If you can work with me to keep this a secret,

359
00:20:36,360 --> 00:20:38,360
when my daughter relies on the royal child,

360
00:20:38,360 --> 00:20:39,960
bringing honor upon herself

361
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,880
and prosperity to our family,

362
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:44,320
our secret affection

363
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:48,720
will surely bring you endless wealth and glory in the future.

364
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:55,560
But if you betray me,

365
00:20:58,280 --> 00:21:02,200
once our shameful affair in the palace

366
00:21:02,280 --> 00:21:03,960
is exposed,

367
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:07,720
these palace walls

368
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:12,760
will be our burial place.

369
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:19,760
Dr. Sun told the Emperor

370
00:21:20,560 --> 00:21:22,840
that Consort Xian's pulse is normal

371
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:24,880
and it's highly likely a boy.

372
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:26,860
The Emperor was so pleased

373
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:29,280
that he went to see Consort Xian.

374
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:31,980
Consort Xian hid a pillow under her dress

375
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:34,520
and faked her pregnancy, deceiving the Emperor.

376
00:21:34,520 --> 00:21:37,160
This act of deceiving the emperor became increasingly severe.

377
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:39,640
Consort Zhao's mother came up with a plan.

378
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:42,400
She asked Eunuch Chen to find four pregnant women,

379
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:44,200
under the pretext of embroidering at home,

380
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,930
and kept them confined all day.

381
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:48,960
Are you also here to embroider?

382
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:51,160
Yes, the pay is good.

383
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:53,280
And they don't mind our inconvenience in moving around.

384
00:21:53,280 --> 00:21:55,120
You just need to sit and embroider.

385
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:56,850
There's no need to walk around.

386
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:59,040
If you embroider the Phoenix Singing pattern,

387
00:21:59,040 --> 00:22:00,640
and it gets selected,

388
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:03,850
you will be rewarded with another five strings of coins.

389
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:06,040
Really?

390
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,560
Ever since these pregnant women entered the palace,

391
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:18,490
they have never been able to leave.

392
00:22:18,600 --> 00:22:21,840
They can only write letters to their families to let them know they are safe.

393
00:22:21,840 --> 00:22:23,920
Please make sure to tell my husband

394
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,600
to take good care of himself.

395
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:27,650
Thank you for your trouble.

396
00:22:28,320 --> 00:22:31,240
Please make sure this gets into my husband's hands.

397
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:55,560
Push hard!

398
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:57,880
It's coming out soon.

399
00:22:57,960 --> 00:23:00,120
Hurry, push hard.

400
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,960
Why hasn't she come out yet?

401
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:06,040
The baby is born!

402
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:08,000
Great! Let's go see her.

403
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,720
Did she give birth?

404
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:19,200
We all want to come see her.

405
00:23:19,280 --> 00:23:21,320
Today is a great day.

406
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:22,640
She just gave birth.

407
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:24,240
She is not feeling well.

408
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:25,920
Alright then.

409
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,440
We'll come back later. Let's go.

410
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:28,840
She is going home soon.

411
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:32,160
After all, she just gave birth. It's inappropriate for her to do these chores.

412
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:33,680
Did she finish her work?

413
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:34,720
No.

414
00:23:34,840 --> 00:23:36,160
But my master is kind.

415
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,560
He still gave her three strings of coins

416
00:23:37,560 --> 00:23:38,840
for good luck.

417
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:42,240
Did she have a boy or a girl?

418
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:43,840
A girl.

419
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,840
A girl. A girl is great.

420
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:48,000
I also want to have a baby girl. Yes.

421
00:23:50,440 --> 00:23:52,440
How did you deal with those people?

422
00:23:52,520 --> 00:23:54,520
I have already buried them.

423
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,840
Keep a close eye on these people.

424
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:58,680
You must have a son.

425
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:00,760
As for the rest,

426
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:03,600
I will handle it all.

427
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:37,280
Why is this book here?

428
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:40,640
Mother.

429
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,360
Mother.

430
00:24:42,520 --> 00:24:44,360
Young Master. Young Master.

431
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,280
Young Master.

432
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:50,120
Don't ruin the scene. Calm down.

433
00:24:54,080 --> 00:24:55,720
What are you going to do?

434
00:24:56,800 --> 00:24:58,160
Autopsy.

435
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:01,200
Mother.

436
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:03,760
Mr. Cao.

437
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:06,400
Lord Li's daughter is a coroner.

438
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:08,800
She likes to study corpses all day.

439
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:10,000
Let her examine it.

440
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:18,840
The nail pierced through the palm.

441
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:22,250
There is obvious bruising and laceration around the wound.

442
00:25:22,320 --> 00:25:24,240
But this is not a fatal injury.

443
00:25:24,360 --> 00:25:28,040
It only causes the victim immense pain.

444
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:32,600
The cuts on her face are uneven,

445
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:35,440
likely caused by a broad-bladed sharp weapon,

446
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:37,320
and made after death.

447
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:42,120
The strangulation mark on her neck is purplish-black

448
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:45,680
with obvious surface peeling and bruising.

449
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:48,320
Judging from its width and depth,

450
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:52,120
the fatal wound should be caused by a thick hemp rope.

451
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:55,960
After death, a dagger was plunged into her chest.

452
00:25:56,200 --> 00:25:58,800
Time of death is within half an hour.

453
00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:01,360
Half an hour?

454
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:04,000
We were all drinking just now.

455
00:26:04,080 --> 00:26:05,760
We didn't leave.

456
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:09,600
The suspect strangled Madam Cao to death here first.

457
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,600
then dragged all the way to the wall.

458
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:15,200
After that, the killer pinned Madam Cao against the wall with their body

459
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:17,200
and nailed her into the wall.

460
00:26:17,280 --> 00:26:19,640
Given the height and strength required,

461
00:26:21,120 --> 00:26:23,560
the suspect is a male.

462
00:26:26,080 --> 00:26:29,200
Who... who could be so cruel,

463
00:26:30,120 --> 00:26:33,040
murdering my mother and torturing her like this?

464
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:38,760
You were the first to find Madam Cao's body.

465
00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:40,280
Don't you stay in the west wing?

466
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:41,880
Why were you in the backyard?

467
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:48,280
You were the first to find her dead!

468
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:51,280
He still has my mother's blood on his hands!

469
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:53,040
My mother refused to fund you,

470
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:54,440
so you killed her in a fit of anger!

471
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:55,840
You are the murderer!

472
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:56,840
Calm down.

473
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:58,440
The authorities will find out the truth.

474
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,880
You can't say that.

475
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:01,490
We are relatives after all.

476
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:03,880
You're wronging me by saying that.

477
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,120
What relative?

478
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:07,640
This man is a distant relative from her maiden family.

479
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:10,080
The relationship is so distant, it's almost nonexistent.

480
00:27:10,080 --> 00:27:12,160
He visited my mother before the banquet

481
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:13,880
to ask for a job,

482
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:16,360
even offering his young daughter to be my concubine.

483
00:27:16,360 --> 00:27:17,320
What?

484
00:27:18,360 --> 00:27:19,280
Listen to me.

485
00:27:19,360 --> 00:27:21,800
I was indeed here to give Madam a gift.

486
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:45,320
Somebody!

487
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:48,200
Although he is obnoxious,

488
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:50,040
he shouldn't be the suspect.

489
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:54,400
That still doesn't prove he's not the killer.

490
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:55,800
For now,

491
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,800
he is still the prime suspect.

492
00:27:57,880 --> 00:28:00,560
Jiang, you can't just say things like that.

493
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,280
Mr. Jiang.

494
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:04,280
I can prove he's not the killer.

495
00:28:04,360 --> 00:28:05,680
Let's hear it.

496
00:28:07,600 --> 00:28:10,440
From the bloody footprints on the ground, we can see that

497
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:13,960
when the witness came to the backyard and approached Madam Cao,

498
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:17,000
his foot had already stepped on the blood.

499
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:19,040
When he saw the body clearly,

500
00:28:19,040 --> 00:28:20,800
he fell to the ground in shock,

501
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:24,400
leaving this footprint with the toe pointing outward.

502
00:28:24,520 --> 00:28:27,080
But this is completely different from the footprint of the killer

503
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:30,640
who approached quietly and escaped safely after the crime.

504
00:28:31,080 --> 00:28:32,720
By comparing the shapes of the footprints,

505
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,800
it can be confirmed that they are not from the same person.

506
00:28:34,800 --> 00:28:37,880
This person's footprint matches this one perfectly.

507
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:42,080
He is the first witness who left such a unique footprint,

508
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:45,960
not the careful and orderly killer.

509
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:47,360
Young Master, did you hear that?

510
00:28:47,360 --> 00:28:49,360
I was wronged! I am not the killer!

511
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,320
I am not the killer!

512
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:52,080
If it wasn't you, who else could it be?

513
00:28:52,080 --> 00:28:53,160
Wait.

514
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:54,760
Where is Master Yuan?

515
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:58,080
No.

516
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:01,800
Just now at the banquet,

517
00:29:01,800 --> 00:29:03,120
he got drunk.

518
00:29:15,600 --> 00:29:17,400
Brother Yuan, are you okay?

519
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,360
I'm fine, I'm fine.

520
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:22,640
Brother Yuan is truly a passionate man.

521
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:24,000
Let me sober up,

522
00:29:24,080 --> 00:29:26,480
then I'll drink to my heart's content with Brother Jiang.

523
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,520
Okay.

524
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:29,560
Be careful.

525
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:32,440
Be careful. Then I'll go inside first.

526
00:29:32,520 --> 00:29:33,720
I'll go inside first.

527
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:35,720
Alright, Brother Yuan, be careful.

528
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:39,260
When I returned to my room,

529
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:40,920
Master Yuan was gone.

530
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:42,920
I thought

531
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:46,920
he was chatting about poetry with you, Scholar Jiang.

532
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:50,000
Yeah, then where did he go?

533
00:29:50,120 --> 00:29:51,680
That I don't know.

534
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:53,160
See? I told you.

535
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:54,760
Everyone, listen to me.

536
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:56,960
Constable Su,

537
00:29:57,120 --> 00:29:59,840
search every inch of this mansion carefully

538
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,920
to find Master Yuan's whereabouts.

539
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:03,400
Alright.

540
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:05,840
Coroner Li,

541
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:09,040
take some men and carry Madam Cao's body back to the guest room.

542
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:10,000
Settle her properly.

543
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:10,920
Alright.

544
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:18,960
Everyone else, come back to the inner hall with me.

545
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:21,090
You all must prove your innocence.

546
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:22,520
Answer truthfully:

547
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:24,200
what did each of you do after returning to your rooms,

548
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:26,160
and who can vouch for you?

549
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:30,000
I was in the inner hall keeping the guests company from beginning to end.

550
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:32,480
During that time, my mother suddenly said she had to leave. I drank too much and was drunk.

551
00:30:32,480 --> 00:30:34,840
I stayed until the last guest left. Scholar Jiang and I both stayed in single rooms.

552
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:38,320
Before going to sleep, I saw the candlelight flickering in the room opposite, and then with the steward's help,

553
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:39,920
he was writing furiously. I just returned to my guest room.

554
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,240
So I went over the commentary I needed to write

555
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:44,040
for the anthology. I then pointed to the backyard.

556
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:47,080
I was in the same room with Constable Su.

557
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,400
After returning to our room,

558
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:50,600
we were both writing reviews.

559
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:53,760
Suddenly, we heard a scream outside.

560
00:30:53,840 --> 00:30:55,800
So we went out to check.

561
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:59,560
We hadn't been anywhere else before that.

562
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,120
Brother Jueming.

563
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:06,520
We found Master Yuan's body in the Zangge Room.

564
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:15,600
What's wrong now?

